  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d3b78c5a08e324884bb0f0a35315554e, type: 3}
  m_Name: Verminform
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::AbilitySO
  abilityName: Verminform
  description: "Take the form of a rat to squeeze into any\nspace that a rat could
    fit into. You return to\nyour normal form as soon as you are in a\nspace that
    allows it. You can also speak with\nrats, who are generally helpful.\nPASSION
    - Trust\nRestore SPI when giving the benefit of the\ndoubt in a way that leaves
    you vulnerable.\nIn squeakling hole I squashed and curled\nAmidst my kin, a kinder
    world\nRat Knight\nMODIFIED ARMOUR\nType Modified for...\n1 Leather Fast donning/removal\n2
    Velvet Fire immunity\n3 Fur Ease of swimming\n4 Scales Total fall protection\n5
    Hair Concealing robes\n6 Straw Repellent to rats\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Rising
    Seer\nVIG 14, CLA 17, SPI 17, 4 GD\n\u2022 Embers of starlight in the form of
    a man,\nstreaks of light soaring upward.\n\u2022 Touch grants glimpses of foresight
    for the\nrest of the day.\n\u2022 Wants to find somebody virtuous enough\nto
    take their place, after which they can\nascend fully to the stars.\nPerson: Antisocial
    haberdasher ~ Name: Abran ~ Characteristic: Prosthetic legs\nObject: Fear egg
    ~ Beast: Lesser mule ~ State: Basking ~ Theme: Carving\n6\n12\nThe"
